          Click on the link to see how to check your answer in Sage. -->Let <m>a=3</m> and then graph the curve <m>\vec T(3,\omega)=(3\cos\omega,9\sin\omega)</m> for <m>\omega\in[0,2\pi]</m>.
          
        </p>
        <p>
          You can use the following SageMath Cell to check your answer.
        </p>
        <sage>
